The '''Hasamadhi warehouse district''' was a sector of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] located near the south pole. It was near the [[Southern Underground/Legends|Southern Underground]], and served as a base for [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] and [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] for a time while they were hiding the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] before staging the rescue of [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] from [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]]. The [[Ice Crypts]] were located several hundred meters below it.

